com.vmware.vapi.std

Class StandardDataFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.std.StandardDataFactory

  • public class StandardDataFactory
extends Object
    Factory for DataDefinitions and DataValues for standard vAPI structures, like errors and localizable messages.

      • createStandardErrorDefinition

        public static com.vmware.vapi.data.ErrorDefinition createStandardErrorDefinition(String errorName)
        Creates ErrorDefinitions for standard vAPI errors. This includes definitions for nested data types such as LocalizableMessage, NestedLocalizableMessage and LocalizationParam too.
        Parameters:
        errorName - the error name
        Returns:
        new ErrorDefinition instance

      • createErrorValueForMessages

                                     List<com.vmware.vapi.Message> messages)
        Creates a standard error ErrorValue instance for the given name list of Messages.
        See Also:
        createErrorValueForMessages(ErrorDefinition, List)

      • createErrorValueForMessages

        public static ErrorValue createErrorValueForMessages(com.vmware.vapi.data.ErrorDefinition errorDef,
                                     List<com.vmware.vapi.Message> messages)
        Creates instance for given error definition and list of Messages.
        Parameters:
        errorDef - error definition
        messages - the messages for the new ErrorValue
        Returns:
        new ErrorValue instance
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if messages or errorDef is null or messages is empty or contains null element(s)

      • getMessagesFromErrorValue

        public static List<com.vmware.vapi.Message> getMessagesFromErrorValue(StructValue error)
        Returns messages associated with the specified standard error ErrorValue represented as list of Messages. This method assumes the structure of "messages" field from createErrorValueForMessages(ErrorDefinition, List). In case this structure is not present - empty list is returned.
        Parameters:
        error - standard error value
        Returns:
        list of Message instances
